title: Card spending change
caption: Daily change in consumer debit and credit card spending in Austin, TX categorized by industry sector. Entries between January 4th - January 31st of 2019 - present is used to determine relative change in entries for subsequent days of the respective year. Subsequently the change is seasonally adjusted where a year-over-year division is carried out between 2019 and other years and is presented as a 7-day moving average. The aforementioned preprocessing steps are performed by the data provider whom is referenced as the source.
